episodes.title: Pastor Gino Jennings Responds to "Woman-Hater" & “Cult” Claims
episodes.description:
Pastor Gino Jennings addresses the accusations that he hates women, hes running a cult — and he’s not holding back. L

Is it misogyny? Or is it Holiness? 👀Some say he’s just quoting the Bible. Others say he’s weaponizing it against women. Either way, Pastor Jennings has time today.

📢 What do you think? Is this tough love or spiritual suppression? Drop your thoughts in the comments and let’s talk about it.
